HEADWORD: Hangnail
<hw>Hang"nail`</hw> <pr>(-n⟦amac⟧l`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[A
corruption of <ets>agnail</ets>.]</ety> <def>A small piece or sliver of
skin which hangs loose, near the root of a finger nail.</def>
<rj><au>Holloway.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
